  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>Yes</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To compare Quality of Life between the ARIMIDEX group, the NOLVADEX group and the ARIMIDEX
      plus NOLVADEX combination group during the first two years of treatment. (a) To compare the
      difference in Quality of Life between the ARIMIDEX group and the NOLVADEX group (b) To
      compare Quality of Life in the ARIMIDEX plus NOLVADEX combination group with the NOLVADEX
      group for non-inferiority; if non inferiority is concluded, the difference in QOL between
      these two groups will be assessed.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
